      "date": "2016-11-16 22:19:44.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nThe patch works but I still can't reactivate the import but I'm still looking into that issue and will handle as a separate patch.\n\n[root@H-340-19 ~]# lctl dl\n  0 UP mgc MGC10.10.10.89@o2ib 4a59f3aa-7f85-01c0-b910-994dadbdb940 5\n  1 UP lov Test1-clilov-ffff8108b4a7d800 d9371638-7895-0e86-7481-a9106bee87d5 4\n  2 UP mdc Test1-MDT0000-mdc-ffff8108b4a7d800 d9371638-7895-0e86-7481-a9106bee87d5 5\n  3 UP osc Test1-OST0000-osc-ffff8108b4a7d800 d9371638-7895-0e86-7481-a9106bee87d5 5\n  4 UP osc Test1-OST0001-osc-ffff8108b4a7d800 d9371638-7895-0e86-7481-a9106bee87d5 4\n  5 UP osc Test1-OST0002-osc-ffff8108b4a7d800 d9371638-7895-0e86-7481-a9106bee87d5 4\n  6 UP osc Test1-OST0003-osc-ffff8108b4a7d800 d9371638-7895-0e86-7481-a9106bee87d5 5\n[root@H-340-19 ~]# lfs check servers\nTest1-MDT0000-mdc-ffff8108b4a7d800: active\nTest1-OST0000-osc-ffff8108b4a7d800: active\nTest1-OST0001-osc-ffff8108b4a7d800: check error: Input/output error\nTest1-OST0002-osc-ffff8108b4a7d800: check error: Input/output error\nTest1-OST0003-osc-ffff8108b4a7d800: active\n[root@H-340-19 ~]# lctl get_param osc.*.import | egrep 'target|state'\n    target: Test1-OST0000_UUID\n    state: FULL\n    target: Test1-OST0001_UUID\n    state: NEW\n    target: Test1-OST0002_UUID\n    state: NEW\n    target: Test1-OST0003_UUID\n    state: FULL",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
